  # Europe’s hottest AI image startup Black Forest Labs bags $300M from a16z, NVIDIA and Salesforce Ventures
  
  [![Sofia Chesnokova](<Base64-Image-Removed>)bySofia Chesnokova](https://techfundingnews.com/author/sofia/ "View all posts by Sofia Chesnokova")
  
  December 1, 2025
  
  2 minute read
  
  ![Black Forest Labs & T.Capital](<Base64-Image-Removed>)
  Image credits: T.Capital LinkedIn
  
