  **・FLUX.1 \[schnell\]**
  
  A refined version of the basic model that runs up to 10 times faster. Licensed under **[Apache 2](https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0)** .
  
  **FLUX.1 \[schnell\] \| AI Playground \| fal.ai**
  
